      <title>卡尼说，加拿大有限匹配美国的关税。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/canada-is-limited-in-matching-further-us-tariffs-carney-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）说，加拿大只有在回应美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对经济体之间的规模不匹配的新税款时才能走得太远。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/canada-is-limited-in-matching-further-us-tariffs-carney-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 21:29:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国顶级法院拒绝更多试图停止债务刹车投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/german-top-court-rejects-more-attempts-to-stop-debt-brake-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国最高法院驳回了额外的企图，以防止国家即将离任的议会对宪法进行更改，以消除国防借贷的限制，并建立了5000亿欧元（5460亿美元）的基础设施基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/german-top-court-rejects-more-attempts-to-stop-debt-brake-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 20:59:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰总理并没有放弃与印度的贸易协定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/new-zealand-pm-hasn-t-given-up-on-dairy-in-trade-deal-with-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里斯托弗·卢克森（Christopher Luxon）说，新西兰已准备好与印度进行一些艰难的谈判，因为它寻求包括乳制品在内的自由贸易协定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/new-zealand-pm-hasn-t-given-up-on-dairy-in-trade-deal-with-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 20:51:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
